text: Dermestops is a genus of leaf beetles in the subfamily Eumolpinae. It contains only one species, Dermestops ahngeri, which is distributed in Turkmenistan. ==References== Category:Eumolpinae Category:Chrysomelidae genera Category:Monotypic beetle genera Category:Beetles of Asia Category:Insects of Central Asia Category:Taxa named by Georgiy Jacobson
